## Core Technologies

This project is built upon several open-source technologies:

### virtnbdbackup
- **Author**: @abbbi
- **Repository**: https://github.com/abbbi/virtnbdbackup
- **Description**: Backup utility for libvirt, using the latest changed block tracking features
- **License**: GPL-3.0
- **Role**: Core backup engine that powers the backup and restore functionality

The virtnbdbackup project provides the fundamental backup capabilities that make this
management system possible. We are deeply grateful to @abbbi and the virtnbdbackup
community for their excellent work.

